				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell will be awesome!  Yah, it does nearly the same dmg as the 20 bolt spell but think about it...it only costs 5 more mana to cast, and by lvl 24 you'll have loads more mana than you would at lvl 20!!  Not to mention it's alot harder to resist than fire based spells, and it stuns casters.  I'm fighting aviaks in Sk right now (I'm lvl 20)and even the yellow rooks will resist the bolt spell, so i decided to do a little test.  I memed that old dusty lvl 8 35 dmg shock spell and i could hit the Aviak Harriers (red to me) for full dmg every time!  I hate the 20 bolt spell.  Besides the shock of blades spells look a lot cooler!  Well that's my 2 cp.<BR>
